name: Kooks
body: This is a no-new-feature update. Instead huge parts of the app have been re-written from the ground up. Transistor now uses ViewModel (Android Architecture Components) to keep data between different app components in sync. As a side effect a lot of little bugs are now gone. If this update introduces new bugs please consider using the Issue Tracker on GitHub (https://github.com/y20k/transistor/issues).
